SOUTHERN REHABILITATION GROUP, PLLC, et al., petitioners,
v.
Kathleen SEBELIUS, Secretary of Health and Human Services, et al. No. 13-1223. Supreme Court of the United States June 9, 2014. Former decision, 732 F.3d 670 .
